## [1.0.0] — 2025-04-28

### Added
- Initial release of the Maze Engineers Research Trend Forecaster
- **9 product categories**: Spatial Memory, Anxiety & Fear, Depression, Social, Motor, Operant, Pain, Zebrafish, Drosophila
- **75+ behavioral test products** with pre-baked PubMed publication trend data (2020–2024)
- **Trend & Forecast view** per product:
  - Annual publication bar chart (2020–2024)
  - 2024 paper count, 5-year growth %, year-over-year change, peak year
  - Trend classification: Rising, Stable, Declining, or Emerging
  - AI demand forecast for 2025 (High / Moderate / Low) with confidence score
  - 3 key research drivers per product
  - Strategic recommendation for Maze Engineers
  - 3 hot research areas
- **Publications view** per product:
  - Up to 8 recent high-impact featured papers (2024–2025)
  - Sorted by journal impact factor descending
  - Color-coded by impact tier (purple / green / yellow / gray)
  - NEW 2025 badge for papers published in 2025
  - Linked titles to PubMed or DOI
  - Live "Search latest papers on PubMed" button per product
- **Species badges** on every product tile: mouse, rat, zebrafish, drosophila
- **Species-matched PubMed queries** for more accurate publication counts
- Keyword data sourced from Maze Engineers product keyword CSV
- Fully self-contained single HTML file — no dependencies, no build step, no API keys
- Local server instructions for Windows, Mac/Linux, and Node.js
- GitHub Pages hosting instructions

### Files
- `index.html` — full application
- `README.md` — documentation
- `LICENSE` — proprietary license
- `.gitignore` — standard ignore rules

